# Normalize line endings: text files are stored LF in the repo regardless of a
# contributor's core.autocrlf. Stops CRLF drift from Windows editors/PowerShell.
# Note: git has no attribute that strips a UTF-8 BOM — that is enforced by the
# check:bom pre-commit guard (scripts/check-bom.mjs). A BOM in package.json
# silently breaks Vite's PostCSS config resolution and blanks the app.
* text=auto

# Binary assets — never normalize line endings or attempt textual diffs.
*.png   binary
*.jpg   binary
*.jpeg  binary
*.webp  binary
*.ico   binary
*.mp4   binary
*.webm  binary
*.woff  binary
*.woff2 binary
